data.title: Prime Ministers Series: Delivering Results for Canadians, with the Right Honourable Jean Chrétien
data.text:
Date and time: March 3, 2020 | 8:45 am to 4:30 pm (EST)

Location: Shaw Centre, 55 Colonel By Drive, Ottawa, Ontario

The 2020 edition featured the Right Honourable Jean Chrétien, who reflected on his experiences as Prime Minister of Canada. The daylong conversation about "Delivering Results for Canadians" offered exclusive insights from speakers who were close to the action, shared lessons learned for the modern public service and explored 4 nation-building themes that evoked tough choices and fierce resistance:
